I"i<p><strong>Volume trading</strong> is a popular technique in cryptocurrency trading.</p>

<p>Volume trading is not particular to crypto markets, it is used on legacy markets as well.</p>

<!--more-->

<p>Broadly, volume trading is any trading technique that takes into account changes in traded volume on a market.</p>

<p>On crypto trading forums, when someone talks about <em>volume trading</em>, it will usually be <em>volume profile trading</em>.</p>

<h3 id="glossary-entries-where-you-can-learn-about-volume-trading">Glossary entries where you can learn about volume trading</h3>

<ul>
  <li><a href="/glossary/vpvr/">VPVR (Volume profile visible range)</a></li>
  <li><a href="/glossary/market-profile/">Market Profile</a></li>
  <li><a href="/glossary/footprint-trading/">Footprint Trading</a></li>
